<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Thu, 10 Feb 2022 11:09:06 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Switch《SD Gundam Battle Alliance》【有片睇】3 人連線組隊 ARPG</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/10/sd-gundam-battle-alliance/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sd-gundam-battle-alliance</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 10 Feb 2022 11:09:06 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[SD Gundam Battle Alliance]]></category><category><![CDATA[SD 高達]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1085642</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Bandai Namco Entertainment 將於今年推出《SD 高達》系列最新作品《SD Gunda [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Bandai Namco Entertainment 將於今年推出《SD 高達》系列最新作品《SD Gundam Battle Alliance》，支援 3 人連線模式，透過一連串冒險與戰鬥修復異常的歷史。</p><p>Bandai Namco Entertainment（萬代南夢宮遊戲）在任天堂舉行的「Nintendo Direct 2022.2.10」中宣布，將於今年推出《SD 高達》系列最新作品《SD Gundam Battle Alliance》（SDガンダム バトルアライアンス）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_03.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_03-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_03-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_03-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_03.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_04.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085683" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_04-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_04-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_04-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/42190_04.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Bandai 官方影片截圖</p><p>《SD Gundam Battle Alliance》是以《SD 高達》系列作題材的全新動作角色扮演遊戲。遊戲以發生異常的歷代《SD 高達》系列的世界作故事背景，玩家需展開冒險與戰鬥，把異常的歷史修復。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.42.11.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.42.11-694x369.png" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.42.11-694x369.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.42.11-1280x681.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.42.11-768x408.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.42.11-1536x817.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.42.11-2048x1089.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.42.11.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.37.32.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.37.32-694x369.png" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.37.32-694x369.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.37.32-1280x681.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.37.32-768x408.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.37.32-1536x817.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.37.32-2048x1089.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.37.32.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.38.39.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.38.39-694x369.png" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.38.39-694x369.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.38.39-1280x681.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.38.39-768x408.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.38.39-1536x817.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.38.39-2048x1089.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.38.39.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Bandai 官方影片截圖</p><p>遊戲中玩家可使用 3 隻機體組隊出擊，有指更能支援與 3 名玩家連線參與多人模式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.15.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.15-694x369.png" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.15-694x369.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.15-1280x681.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.15-768x408.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.15-1536x817.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.15-2048x1089.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.15.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.29.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.29-694x369.png" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.29-694x369.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.29-1280x681.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.29-768x408.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.29-1536x817.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.29-2048x1089.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 6.39.29.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Bandai 官方影片截圖</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_85039"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j12f4rP6ao4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://www.4gamer.net/games/617/G061734/20220210005/">4Gamer.net</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
