</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>任天堂《Nintendo Switch Sports》　《Wii Sports》式動作追蹤及體感玩法</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/10/nintendo-switch-sports-wii-sports/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=nintendo-switch-sports-wii-sports</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 10 Feb 2022 07:46:14 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nintendo Switch Sports]]></category><category><![CDATA[Wii Sports]]></category><category><![CDATA[任天堂]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1085570</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>任天堂（Nintendo）將於 4 月 29 日推出全新遊戲《Nintendo Switch Sports》， [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>任天堂（Nintendo）將於 4 月 29 日推出全新遊戲《Nintendo Switch Sports》，一如以往《Wii Sports》般，透過動作追蹤技術為玩家提供網球、護身道、及足球等，多款體感運動遊戲。</p><p>《Nintendo Switch Sports》秉承了《Wii Sports》的經典概念，利用動作追蹤技術的體感玩法，透過 Switch joy-con 遊戲手掣分析玩家動作。除了為玩家提供網球、保齡球、護身道等多種《Wii Sports》遊戲外，更另加入足球、羽毛球、及排球遊戲。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.39.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.39-694x344.png" alt="" width="694" height="344" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.39-694x344.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.39-1280x634.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.39-768x381.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.39-1536x761.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.39-2048x1015.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.39.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.18.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085573" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.18-694x344.png" alt="" width="694" height="344" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.18-694x344.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.18-1280x634.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.18-768x381.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.18-1536x761.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.18-2048x1015.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.20.18.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.31.25.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085577" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.31.25-694x369.png" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.31.25-694x369.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.31.25-1280x681.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.31.25-768x408.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.31.25-1536x817.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.31.25-2048x1089.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-10-下午 1.31.25.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">任天堂官方影片截圖</p><p>《Nintendo Switch Sports》將於 4 月 29 日正式發布，而訂閱了任天堂 Switch Online 的用戶，則可提前於 2 月 18 日至 20 日測試遊戲。參與測試的玩家可率先試玩保齡球、護身道及網球遊戲，惟不能與朋友連線對戰，只可隨機匹配對戰對象。</p><p><a href="http